ision\n2. Small loans affected most significantly"]},{"id":"F-007","severity":"Medium","confidence":"medium","title":"No Validation of Collateral Token in _borrowOrTrade","locations":["0x9e1341a201b1aecb1b0dd584989790a0232b4af5/Contract.sol:1769-1830"],"claim":"The _borrowOrTrade function does not validate that the loan params exist before using loanParamsIds mapping. Invalid params would be passed to the protocol.","impact":"Could lead to revert or unexpected behavior when using unregistered collateral tokens.","paths":["1. Call borrow with unregistered collateral token\n2. loanParamsIds lookup returns 0 bytes32\n3. Protocol call fails or uses invalid params"]},{"id":"F-008","severity":"Low","confidence":"medium","title":"Missing Return Value Checks for Non-Standard ERC20","locations":["0x9e1341a201b1aecb1b0dd584989790a0232b4af5/Contract.sol:15-27"],"claim":"The IERC20 interface defines transfer/transferFrom returning bool, but some tokens (like USDT) don't return values on transfer functions. The _callOptionalReturn handles this but silently accepts no return.","impact":"Transfers may silently fail with non-standard tokens that don't return bool.","paths":["1. Interact with non-standard ERC20\n2. Transfer appears to succeed but actually fails\n3. Funds lost or stuck"]},{"id":"F-009","severity":"Low","confidence":"medium","title":"No Access Control on Pausable Functions","locations":["0x9e1341a201b1aecb1b0dd584989790a0232b4af5/Contract.sol:668-689"],"claim":"The pausable modifier checks if a function is paused but doesn't specify who can pause. The pause mechanism is not visible in this contract.","impact":"If anyone can pause functions, users could be locked out of their funds.","paths":["1. Unknown party pauses critical functions\n2. Users cannot withdraw or trade"]},{"id":"F-010","severity":"Low","confidence":"medium","title":"Hardcoded Protocol Addresses Cannot Be Updated","locations":["0x9e1341a201b1aecb1b0dd584989790a0232b4af5/Contract.sol:901-902"],"claim":"